 it or remove the dependency array.",["737"],"Assignments to the 'productType' variable from inside React Hook useEffect will be lost after each render. To preserve the value over time, store it in a useRef Hook and keep the mutable value in the '.current' property. Otherwise, you can move this variable directly inside useEffect.",{"range":"738","text":"725"},"'useEffect' is defined but never used.","no-dupe-keys","Duplicate key 'right'.","ObjectExpression",{"range":"739","text":"725"},"React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'searchPlaces'. Either include it or remove the dependency array. If 'searchPlaces' changes too often, find the parent component that defines it and wrap that definition in useCallback.",["740"],"'setShowWhatsTheRush' is assigned a value but never used.","'showViralDeals' is assigned a value but never used.","'setShowViralDeals' is assigned a value but never used.","'getShareLink' is assigned a value but never used.",{"range":"741","text":"725"},"The href attribute requires a valid value to be accessible. Provide a valid, navigable address as the href value. If you cannot provide a valid href, but still need the element to resemble a link, use a button and change it with appropriate styles. Learn more: https://github.com/jsx-eslint/eslint-plugin-jsx-a11y/blob/HEAD/docs/rules/anchor-is-valid.md","'basketData' is assigned a value but never used.","'setBasketData' is assigned a value but never used.","'isClient' is assigned a value but never used.",["742"],"'setOrigProducts' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'categoriesList'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["743"],"'logoSrc' is assigned a value but never used.",["744"],{"range":"745","text":"725"},"'ProductCard' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'fetchViralDeals'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.",["746"],["747"],["748"],{"range":"749","text":"725"},"'ta